{"tid":1467824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今日機場一樣可以係我地既彈藥","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:22:16.000Z","uid":219042,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef54f429600791f22e5af2976ae325430eea5da","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"一上熱門睇 全部都係啲散發失敗言論既post<br />\n真係睇到扯火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼個冇大台既運動 始終唔同人有唔同諗法 實際遇到問題又會出現唔同處理方法 我地唔可以下下要求完美 要求唔出錯<br />\n好似今日咁 出咗少少問題就又割蓆 又話輸又盛咁<br />\n個個咁諗就死得啦<br />\n<br />\n其實今次捉左成晚鬼 歸根究低都係大家對鬼既恐懼<br />\n點解會恐懼？<br />\n因為臥底係冇任何資料 社會大眾完全唔知臥底實際做咗啲咩 幾時開始滲透 有冇發起/鼓吹任何暴力行為 臥底完全可以做任何違法/冇道德既行徑已唔需要付出任何代價/法律責任 因為黑警唔會透露 咁樣我地捉鬼真係好過份咩？<br />\n<br />\n我相信處理尼件事仲有好多方法 我只係提出自己一個少少既睇法 但個重點係 唔好一有事就屌 一係事就割 咁樣係解決唔到問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d8515c28747fa7ef28e9b8eae5d81e50953f0c","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"10推"},{"pid":"111fc8fda515e952006d97d34616d094ab009693","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"9推"},{"pid":"13b140343ed617adb1c457e8107d96ecafcf7803","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:26.000Z","msg":"8推"},{"pid":"bf2ecbce0ee6a78c9ee05b031c1500635dc23251","tid":1467824,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"諗計仔<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"571e7190d6f6f67f67c1bf2db754dfd440ec36c9","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"7推"},{"pid":"45e932ded7e7c797aa3682e955d4ab7e3e64e4e2","tid":1467824,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"禮貌版<br />\n前線你好！核彈我也不會割。天琦說過與港共鬥爭不能有任何底線。既然有鬼捉不了已成事實(亦得到官方承認)，何不反其道而行，將一切大眾不能接受的行為推卸給popo(注意！並非割！)有了這免死金牌，前線能放下民意顧慮，盡情去做該做的事(不要斷正就可以)。你們的背後有我們！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誠狠版<br />\n屌你老母，醒少少好唔好?班差佬畀咗咁大 個核彈你都唔識玩?！ 天琦講過你班撚屌唔好有任何潔癖， 咁撚正氣點打中共啲陰招。示威肯定有鬼， 捉嚟都嘥鳩氣。 用下你個豬腦逆向思維咁諗， 有咩事咪奶撚落曬啲臥底到囉。 大眾淨係需要一個合理到嘅版本，陰謀論冇所謂㗎。 拎撚住依個免死金牌， 前線手足咪可以放手做，文宣我哋咪可以輕鬆打囉。 屌你老母，對面元朗嗰時已經做緊謠，唔係唔撚返佢哋呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"bf872755314785ba5ccdb84fb6445f0e48a75fc9","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"6推"},{"pid":"8f7871cc1099b99f48144c340e8fa08162c41fae","tid":1467824,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"係何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句建議姐818<br />\n好多手足受傷 被捕 點解我地仲企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因 為 未 完 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818見</span>"},{"pid":"96c08bdc257be88b67bda377577b844c3ce8c508","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"5推"},{"pid":"63ed4c806c7b0c6746ccd3b66f4fd8d5a468f047","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"c7c30f777a6afbd2260d0ddc6fdede4c8807c04d","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:28.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"e2d6892d9d97679a6b5c71584078bae93273307a","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"fffc4d5627061ceef7eeceb53f4d52b12e276fbd","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01ad4f458896de872b636e316cbe9ca7112f7d2f","tid":1467824,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:50.000Z","msg":"［我屌晒你地老母］成個運動俾D鬼搞彎晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e58a76004b9401af1d4851578b27063e521b0889","tid":1467824,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"推，當年蔣介石就係輸畀中共嘅分化，我哋今次都捱得過嘅話，將會迎接最終嘅勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33475a822d42015f6126a21e0e43132416ed465a","tid":1467824,"uid":114550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人冇輸"},{"pid":"21246f12ff2c3a277202c9cdb96a79c43907339e","tid":1467824,"uid":219042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"5毛帶風向都算<br />\n香港人自己唔好跟住